value: Breeds on Cabbage Tree Island, New South Wales. Populations intermediate between leucoptera and brevipes, or forming undescribed races, occur on the Solomons, New Caledonia, New Hebrides, and in subfossil deposits on Lord Howe Island, and have been collected at sea east to the vicinity of the Galapagos and south on beaches of New Zealand.^
